where DTE was going

00:37:50.620 --> 00:37:54.550
to buy our solar energy,
any excess that we use.

00:37:54.550 --> 00:37:56.335
So we're benefiting
greatly financially.

00:37:56.335 --> 00:38:00.010
And that's what's available
in Germany, where there

00:38:00.010 --> 00:38:04.710
was a day this past summer, last
year, where Germany, over half

00:38:04.710 --> 00:38:07.570
of the energy
during this day was

00:38:07.570 --> 00:38:09.380
produced by renewable energy.

00:38:09.380 --> 00:38:15.010
They have a goal to take the
