00:40:01.930 --> 00:40:03.940
That's just--
honestly, I don't know

00:40:03.940 --> 00:40:07.215
what the motives are
for that world of people

00:40:07.215 --> 00:40:10.920
who are trying to debunk these
technologies that are proven.

00:40:10.920 --> 00:40:13.500
There are life cycle assessments
on all of this stuff.

00:40:13.500 --> 00:40:15.620
And certainly for
certain processes.

00:40:15.620 --> 00:40:17.924
Some manufacturers are
more efficient than others.

00:40:17.924 --> 00:40:19.840
There's actually a
standard now in California,

00:40:19.840 --> 00:40:25.005
