00:41:22.423 --> 00:41:23.310
in the area.

00:41:23.310 --> 00:41:23.840
So there's definitely plenty.

00:41:23.840 --> 00:41:25.090
I don't want to discourage you.

00:41:25.090 --> 00:41:26.200
Because there's plenty of
homes that are doing it now.

00:41:26.200 --> 00:41:28.100
And there are ways of doing it.

00:41:28.100 --> 00:41:30.950
You can actually be creative
and sell your renewable energy

00:41:30.950 --> 00:41:34.030
credits in other states,
and all this other stuff.

00:41:34.030 --> 00:41:35.230
So it's getting crazy.

