00:43:07.760 --> 00:43:10.290
for us, because we knew we were
going to stay in the house,

00:43:10.290 --> 00:43:12.790
that it was going to be the
most efficient and comfortable

00:43:12.790 --> 00:43:14.500
that we could have.

00:43:14.500 --> 00:43:20.670
And then we did get a historic
preservation tax credit,

00:43:20.670 --> 00:43:22.740
which hopefully will
come in the mail

00:43:22.740 --> 00:43:26.760
this next week, for about
